'''小威廉·聖本篤'''（{{lang-en|William San Bento Jr.}}；{{bd|1946年|12月11日|2016年|9月12日}}），是美國的[[民主黨_(美國)|民主黨]]政治人物，前{{le|羅德島州眾議院|Rhode Island House of Representatives}}議員<ref name="RIL">{{cite web |url= http://www.rilin.state.ri.us/representatives/SanBento |title= Representative William San Bento, Jr. |publisher= [[Rhode_Island_General_Assembly|Rhode Island General Assembly]] |location= [[Providence,_Rhode_Island|Providence, Rhode Island]] |accessdate= March 5, 2014 |archive-date= 2020-05-03 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200503193102/http://www.rilin.state.ri.us/representatives/SanBento |dead-url= yes }}</ref>。

==生平==
聖本篤在[[罗德岛州|罗德岛州]][[波塔基特_(罗得岛州)|波塔基特]]出生，擁有一家保險公司<ref name="PVS">{{cite web |url= http://votesmart.org/candidate/biography/7413 |title= William San Bento's Biography |publisher= [[Project_Vote_Smart|Project Vote Smart]] |accessdate= March 5, 2014}}</ref>。

1992年，前羅德島州眾議院第七十五選區議員[[哈維·古萊特|哈維·古萊特]]辭去職務令議席空缺，聖本篤於1992年9月15日的黨內初選勝出，其後以1,801張選票於1992年11月3日的選舉中獲勝當選州眾議員<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.elections.ri.gov/elections/results/1992/rireps.php |title= 1992 Vote for Rhode Island House of Representatives |publisher= Secretary of State of Rhode Island |location= Providence, Rhode Island |accessdate= March 5, 2014 |archive-date= 2017-01-08 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170108035143/http://www.elections.ri.gov/elections/results/1992/rireps.php |dead-url= yes }}</ref>。此後他任職至2003年1月，就因為選區重劃而轉戰第五十八選區，於2002年9月10日的黨內初選勝出<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.elections.ri.gov/elections/results/2002/statewideprimary/staterepdem.php |title= 2002 Representatives in General Assembly, Democrat |publisher= Secretary of State of Rhode Island |location= Providence, Rhode Island |accessdate= March 5, 2014 |archive-date= 2017-01-01 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170101085409/http://www.elections.ri.gov/elections/results/2002/statewideprimary/staterepdem.php |dead-url= no }}</ref>，並以1,874張選票擊敗前[[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]]籍前第五十八選區眾議員[[瑞內·默納德_(政治人物)|瑞內·默納德]]當選<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.elections.ri.gov/elections/results/2002/generalelection/disrep.php |title= 2002 Rhode Island Representatives by Representative District |publisher= Secretary of State of Rhode Island |location= Providence, Rhode Island |accessdate= March 5, 2014 |archive-date= 2018-11-27 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20181127133222/http://www.elections.ri.gov/elections/results/2002/generalelection/disrep.php |dead-url= no }}</ref>，連任五次後到2015年1月卸任<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.pawtuckettimes.com/news/former-house-rep-san-bento-dies-at-age/article_cc6eed90-7bba-11e6-8959-1f570c35e1ad.html |title=Former House Rep. San Bento dies at age 69 |accessdate=2017-03-03 |archive-date=2019-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190615235132/https://www.pawtuckettimes.com/news/former-house-rep-san-bento-dies-at-age/article_cc6eed90-7bba-11e6-8959-1f570c35e1ad.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

